Resource Profile: CARINBBExplanationOfBenefitPharmacy

This profile is used for Explanation of Benefits (EOBs) based on claims submitted by retail pharmacies. The claims data is based on submission standards adopted by the Department of Health and Human Services defined by NCPDP (National Council for Prescription Drug Program)

The official URL for this profile is: 

http://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/StructureDefinition/CARIN-BB-ExplanationOfBenefit-Pharmacy

Formal Views of Profile Content

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.

  • Differential Table
  • Snapshot Table
  • All

This structure is derived from CARINBBExplanationOfBenefit

Summary

Mandatory: 2 elements (15 nested mandatory elements)
Must-Support: 2 elements
Prohibited: 7 elements

Structures

This structure refers to these other structures:

  • http://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/StructureDefinition/CARIN-BB-Organization

Slices

This structure defines the following Slices:

  • The element ExplanationOfBenefit.supportingInfo is sliced based on the value of value:category.coding.code
  • The element ExplanationOfBenefit.item.adjudication is sliced based on the value of value:category.coding.code (Closed)
  • The element ExplanationOfBenefit.adjudication is sliced based on the value of value:category.coding.code (Closed)
